Package: spiritR
Title: Template for clinical trial protocol
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Aaron",
           family = "Conway",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "aaron.conway@utoronto.ca",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9583-8636"))
Description: This package contains an R Markdown template for a clinical trial 
    protocol adhering to the [SPIRIT](http://www.spirit-statement.org/) 
    checklist. It also contains functions to create a xml document containing
    the required information and upload it to clinicaltrials.gov.
